564
00:34:13,719 --> 00:34:15,860
whether you are family, friends, or lovers,

565
00:34:15,860 --> 00:34:18,239
your bond with them will definitely last forever.

566
00:34:18,239 --> 00:34:19,130
Feel it.

567
00:34:21,409 --> 00:34:22,270
Let me take a look.

568
00:34:22,270 --> 00:34:23,350
Okay, thank you.

569
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:26,420
Boss,

570
00:34:27,310 --> 00:34:28,370
I'd like these two.

571
00:34:29,690 --> 00:34:30,659
Good choice.

572
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:33,250
May your bond last forever!

573
00:34:39,659 --> 00:34:40,989
What are you looking at?

574
00:34:42,110 --> 00:34:43,480
Watching them clean.

575
00:34:45,260 --> 00:34:47,409
What's so interesting about cleaning?

576
00:34:47,409 --> 00:34:48,370
Youth.

577
00:34:49,760 --> 00:34:51,100
Once you grow up,

578
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:52,969
you can never go back to it.

579
00:34:57,530 --> 00:34:59,030
Zhao Xiaoxi.

580
00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:00,890
Jenny Yang.

581
00:35:01,490 --> 00:35:02,080
How is it?

582
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:03,680
How does it feel to come back and be a teacher?

583
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:04,680
What do you think?

584
00:35:04,820 --> 00:35:06,090
Not bad, right?

585
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,810
Thank you for your help.

586
00:35:07,990 --> 00:35:08,950
You're welcome.

587
00:35:10,700 --> 00:35:13,850
Is this the friend you mentioned that you met abroad?

588
00:35:14,260 --> 00:35:15,860
Why don't you introduce him?

589
00:35:16,730 --> 00:35:19,390
Mr. Lin... from the History Department.

590
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,720
Hello, I'm Yang Jing.

591
00:35:21,830 --> 00:35:22,830
I teach English.

592
00:35:22,860 --> 00:35:24,060
You may call me Jenny.

593
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:24,930
Jenny.

594
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,340
Hello, I'm Benny.

595
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:30,180
How's school? Are you settling in well?

596
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:32,100
Not bad.

597
00:35:32,350 --> 00:35:33,080
That's good.

598
00:35:34,090 --> 00:35:35,600
I'll get back to work.

599
00:35:35,830 --> 00:35:37,020
If you need anything,

600
00:35:37,020 --> 00:35:38,260
you can contact me later.

601
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:38,890
I'm going.

602
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:39,780
Okay, thank you.

603
00:35:39,780 --> 00:35:40,390
Bye.

604
00:35:44,710 --> 00:35:47,110
You're quite close with Jenny, aren't you?

605
00:35:47,390 --> 00:35:49,120
We went to the same high school.

606
00:35:49,130 --> 00:35:52,980
Since returning from abroad, she's the only person I've kept in touch with.

607
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:56,370
I came back to become a substitute teacher because of her as well.

608
00:35:56,370 --> 00:35:58,100
Does this count as being close?

609
00:35:58,770 --> 00:35:59,420
Yes.

610
00:36:16,190 --> 00:36:17,520
Candied green mangoes.

611
00:36:18,430 --> 00:36:20,580
Sweet and sour. It was my favorite snack when I was a kid.

612
00:36:20,580 --> 00:36:23,180
Since I went to Shanghai, I've rarely had them.

613
00:36:29,700 --> 00:36:32,020
Delicious food should be shared with good friends.

614
00:36:32,020 --> 00:36:32,750
Have a piece.

615
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:35,300
Come on.

616
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,420
I don't eat snacks.

617
00:36:51,430 --> 00:36:52,890
You're such a picky eater,

618
00:36:54,780 --> 00:36:56,510
yet you like this kind of snack?

619
00:36:58,120 --> 00:36:59,520
Because it's delicious.

620
00:36:59,840 --> 00:37:00,680
Oh, right.

621
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:02,930
Why did you suddenly yank me away?

622
00:37:02,940 --> 00:37:05,800
I missed my dad's grand proposal all because of you.

623
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:09,320
I was afraid that you might ruin it.

624
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:11,230
No way!

625
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:13,990
I was going to help them.

626
00:37:14,430 --> 00:37:16,570
Blowing some bubbles on the side for them

627
00:37:16,570 --> 00:37:17,900
and singing some songs.

628
00:37:18,470 --> 00:37:20,530
My dad was so clumsy when he proposed.

629
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:21,590
I was so worried.

630
00:37:33,240 --> 00:37:33,940
But

631
00:37:35,450 --> 00:37:37,310
if your mom agrees to marry my dad,

632
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:40,080
we'll become real brothers.

633
00:37:42,290 --> 00:37:43,890
Will you be upset about this?

634
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:58,320
Help me tie the bracelet.

635
00:37:58,940 --> 00:37:59,800
I want this one.

636
00:37:59,870 --> 00:38:01,330
I'll tie this on you later.

637
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:08,490
You know?

638
00:38:08,970 --> 00:38:10,370
Actually, I always think

639
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:14,850
that the Guanyin Mountain by the Tamsui River is quite spiritual.

640
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:17,480
As long as you pray to it with all your heart,

641
00:38:17,910 --> 00:38:19,510
it will fulfill your wishes.

642
00:38:23,450 --> 00:38:24,060
Come on.

643
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:44,830
So,

644
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:48,510
let's live on campus together.

645
00:38:49,250 --> 00:38:49,970
You and I,

646
00:38:50,950 --> 00:38:51,550
together.

647
00:38:56,730 --> 00:38:57,570
Why?

648
00:38:59,650 --> 00:39:02,580
Because that will be a place that truly belongs to you.

649
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:03,330
Am I right?

650
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:04,920
A real home.

651
00:39:07,860 --> 00:39:09,480
Compared to staying with your dad for a while,

652
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:10,760
with your mom,

653
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:12,140
and with Old Ding,

654
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:16,550
never knowing when you can unpack your luggage

655
00:39:16,780 --> 00:39:18,310
or whether you should pack,

656
00:39:19,490 --> 00:39:20,400
school

657
00:39:21,470 --> 00:39:24,060
is actually the most reassuring place for you.

658
00:39:24,060 --> 00:39:26,450
Although you can't stay in the dorm forever,

659
00:39:26,450 --> 00:39:28,690
at least you'll have a clear timeline.

660
00:39:29,830 --> 00:39:32,870
A place that gives you a sense of belonging and security,

661
00:39:32,870 --> 00:39:34,530
one that truly belongs to you,

662
00:39:35,830 --> 00:39:37,630
is something you'd want, right?

663
00:39:42,550 --> 00:39:43,560
So, you and I,

664
00:39:44,100 --> 00:39:44,860
together.

665
00:39:51,100 --> 00:39:51,830
Okay.

666
00:39:57,410 --> 00:39:58,320
You know what?

667
00:39:58,350 --> 00:40:01,420
I found it when I was peeking at your lyrical writing guide

668
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:03,880
that wrapping one arm around one's shoulder

669
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:05,300
signifies friendship.

670
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:07,680
But I think we are more than friends;

671
00:40:09,990 --> 00:40:10,990
we're family.

672
00:40:23,870 --> 00:40:26,670
Was Big Mouth Xu called that when he was very young?

673
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:29,550
He already had a big mouth when he was a kid,

674
00:40:29,730 --> 00:40:31,790
but we all called him Little Mouth Xu.

675
00:40:32,690 --> 00:40:34,090
You call him Big Mouth Xu?

676
00:40:34,630 --> 00:40:35,630
No.

677
00:40:36,660 --> 00:40:38,920
At least we never call him that in public.

678
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:41,210
But we call his son Little Mouth Xu.

679
00:40:46,700 --> 00:40:47,400
Eat up. Hurry up.

680
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,580
Have more vegetables. Hurry up.

681
00:40:48,580 --> 00:40:49,070
It's good.

682
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:50,280
Don't be picky.

683
00:40:50,740 --> 00:40:52,230
Wang, here.

684
00:40:54,740 --> 00:40:55,550
Give me some.

685
00:40:56,550 --> 00:40:58,050
Of course.

686
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:58,980
Thank you.

687
00:41:09,410 --> 00:41:10,360
Eat more.

688
00:41:11,090 --> 00:41:11,930
You too.

689
00:41:11,950 --> 00:41:14,150
Exams also require physical strength.

690
00:41:14,730 --> 00:41:15,350
Dad.

691
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:19,280
Why are you suddenly calling me "Dad"?

692
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:21,280
Didn't you always call me Old Sheng?

693
00:41:21,330 --> 00:41:22,130
What's wrong?

694
00:41:22,530 --> 00:41:25,750
We have something to tell you.

695
00:41:30,870 --> 00:41:31,690
-Mom.
-Dad.

696
00:41:31,860 --> 00:41:36,660
-We've decided to live on campus together.
-We've decided to live on campus together.

697
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,380
-Live on campus?
-Live on campus?

698
00:41:40,500 --> 00:41:41,780
Are you kidding me?

699
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:43,950
Why live on campus when you have a home?

700
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:45,170
No!

701
00:41:48,570 --> 00:41:50,700
God has taken away people's timidity.

702
00:41:50,950 --> 00:41:54,130
Young boys' love is both passionate and intense.

703
00:41:55,820 --> 00:41:57,450
At that moment, the setting sun cast its light

704
00:41:57,450 --> 00:41:59,050
on the winding Tamsui River.

705
00:41:59,170 --> 00:42:01,280
The patterned window is rimmed with gold.

706
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:04,680
The feathers on the keychain are outlined in a dazzling glow.

707
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:07,410
Time passes as gently and enduringly

708
00:42:08,080 --> 00:42:10,700
as this blessing does.

709
00:42:13,680 --> 00:42:14,890
Change your clothes and let's have breakfast.

710
00:42:14,380 --> 00:42:19,060
[Jiang Tian's Very Moment]

711
00:42:17,160 --> 00:42:17,950
Well...

712
00:42:18,270 --> 00:42:20,070
Wait a minute. I'm not ready yet.

713
00:42:28,840 --> 00:42:30,700
I forgot my phone in the bathroom.

714
00:43:00,850 --> 00:43:03,700
No wonder someone would block himself with a book

715
00:43:04,110 --> 00:43:05,210
and bend down.

